Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界各地的地壳变动渐趋剧烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神话型Aquarion被解除封印的影响现已波及全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又无法知悉阿马塔他们的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能用预备机体前往Altair把它夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是次元门不开我们还能有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给次元空间开个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是偶然获得的能力 加上那时有修雷特帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此 我还是成功过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不试一下 迄今为止我都是为了什么在挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去吧 理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪·W·霍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的力量上孤注一掷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要妨碍我吗 太阳之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是确保真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开对核心单元的直接攻击 只剥夺其战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云这家伙 少瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是太阳之翼的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:01:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能瞬间摧毁GNIS机体的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就加倍奉还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是反弹攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就再次逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的反弹攻击正逐渐被抵消
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云 我死也不会把臭女人交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么如此执着于这个Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她是我的…只属于我的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云大人 我来支援您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台Abductor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altair的未来与出云大人同在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定要平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是男生的合体真是久违了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要到达目标地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 全是男生的杀伐合体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有这样的合体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是激情澎湃的壮士合体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你的身体变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一定会去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前说过的吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞是…洞是为了连接世界而开启的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会连通你所身处的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 在你的心房也开一个大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个足以容下我的大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拟次元门出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才有谁在呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我的名字叫Mi·xy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 坐在上面的是Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 可恶的出云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝相反方向起飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到一下子就碰上了激战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两台Abductor和神话型Aquarion 都是谁在操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 是怪炎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会和这个家伙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是Mix的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两台Abductor企图要掳走御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔和修雷特怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和阿马塔失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在次元的狭缝中奏响了最后的乐曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 那时候的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要阻碍出云大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我回去?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想起来吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起我 想起我安迪·W·霍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话令我不快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看清局势吧 神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不想拯救Altair吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和星球的未来没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想和臭女人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算与全世界为敌 我也不会放开臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了一个Igler…一个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤我的声音是从那里传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星球 大地 和沉睡着的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今 这一切即将要苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳之翼的复活是一柄双刃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会化为分割世界的力量 还是连接世界的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空间补填
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从刚才开始就在重复同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直重复下去 直至将Mix拥入怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挖洞 Mix来填
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是通过这样互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断重复这种无谓之举的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 终于能见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初明明就抛弃了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我一直以来是以怎样的心情生活的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而到了现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不奢求你的原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我希望你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当初抛弃你的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的爸爸不是地球上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名叫出云·神吕木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Altair的最高领导人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了给夏娃的诅咒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给纠缠着Rare·Igler的悲剧画上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸身负带回能承受次元转移的女性的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我还是个演员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她救了因系统故障而迫降到Vega的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快我就察觉到艾丽西亚就是我们所需要的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比那更短的时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相互吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法嘲笑神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曾经因为一个女人而企图背叛Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向高层部门隐瞒了她的存在并返回了Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这没能瞒过未影的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数年后 当他再次出现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 从出云那里听说了夏娃的诅咒之后 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不知道Rare·Igler在那边会遭到何种对待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能帮到你的话 我没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽西亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了要不要带你一起去而犹豫了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更担心你在未知的星球上会遇到什么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这竟然会演变成如此长久的分离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抛弃了你是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要拯救深爱的人的星球 拯救他所爱的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在憎恨着你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我憎恨的是那时候只能眼睁睁看着一切发生的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追寻着自己所爱的人的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有 而我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样而已 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你纠缠够了吧 出云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让艾丽西亚白白牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神话型Aquarion在战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在交战的是出云和另一个你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说神乐?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母亲奥莉莎所建造的Iron C
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的线?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altair的全部能量都渐渐汇聚到Afura Gnis身上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母星总力战炮（Altair Cannon）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这光芒就是Altair所拥有的力量本身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那仅仅是警告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不交出真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次我将会全力发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的 创圣的无限拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 出云
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股力量…未影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你这家伙搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也听说了你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我去艾丽西亚的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有资格请求你原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…把你的母亲从你身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜉蝣?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候曾经见过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为没有了雌性 应该早已绝种了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是337区
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Iron C故障频发的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…Iron C本身就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲般的大地 大地的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来丰收之恩泽的大地 象征着女性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女和男 阴和阳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为有这两极 森罗万象的一切秩序才得以维持
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和大地亦然 星球和宇宙亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Iron C是从星球的大地摄取出能量的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但同时也可能因此夺去了星球母性的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话 Iron C就是一切的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的一生岂不是全都白费了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点 我们好不容易才见到面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有白费
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的一生绝对没有白费
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你把阿马塔带到了这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子肯定会拯救两个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 你是我们相爱的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 你也去爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去爱那个你比任何人都要珍视的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命运中的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经知道你真正的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 我爱你 希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.57,0:24:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要紧抱住你的一切
